text: John David Jackson (born November 18, 1977), better known as Fabolous, is an American rapper. He was born in Brooklyn, New York City. He released his first album, Ghetto Fabolous, in 2001. ==Other websites== * Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Musicians from Brooklyn Category:African- American singers Category:African-American rappers Category:American hip hop singers Category:Rappers from New York (state) Category:American crime victims Category:Gangsta rappers Category:Pseudonyms Category:Singer-songwriters from New York City
